# IMPORTANT VIVA QUESTIONS
# ==========================================

# Q1. What is graph coloring?
# Ans:
# Assign colors to vertices such that
# no adjacent vertices have same color.


# Q2. Which algorithm is used?
# Ans:
# Greedy Algorithm.


# Q3. Why greedy?
# Ans:
# Because we choose first available color
# at every step.


# Q4. What is adjacency matrix?
# Ans:
# Matrix representation of graph.


# Q5. What does 1 mean?
# Ans:
# Edge exists.


# Q6. What does 0 mean?
# Ans:
# No edge.


# Q7. Why diagonal is 0?
# Ans:
# Node is not connected to itself.


# Q8. What is solution dictionary?
# Ans:
# Stores node and assigned color.


# Q9. What is used list?
# Ans:
# Stores colors already used
# by neighboring nodes.


# Q10. Time complexity?
# Ans:
# O(V²)
